"BlockBlast.instructions" = "# Block Blast!\n\nFit pieces onto an 8×8 grid and clear lines for points.\n\n## How to play\n\n- Three pieces are offered at the bottom of the screen at a time.\n- **Drag** a piece onto the grid. The board highlights where it will land.\n- Drop the piece onto a valid spot to place it.\n- When you complete a **full row**, **full column**, or **3×3 box**, those cells **clear**.\n- New pieces appear when all three have been placed.\n\n## Scoring\n\n- Each placed cell scores points.\n- Clearing rows, columns, or 3×3 boxes scores **bonus** points — clearing **multiple at once** scores even more.\n- **Clearing the entire board** awards a big bonus.\n\n## Game over\n\nThe game ends when none of the three offered pieces fits anywhere on the board.";
"Version %@ (%@)" = "Version %1$@ (%2$@)";
